title: Microsoft Office 2010 VL ProPlus English (x64) July 2016
description:
Microsoft Office 2010 VL ProPlus English (x64) July 2016

Release Info

- Language: English (en-US)
- Channel: Volume License
- Version 14.0.7166.5000 (SP2)
- Architectures: x64
- Proofing Tools: English, French, Spanish
- Updated July 12, 2016

Bonus folder

- KMSpico 10.2.0 Final + Portable
- Microsoft Toolkit 2.6 BETA 5
- Classic Menu for Office v5.85 (adds Office 2003 type toolbars and menus to Office 2013)
- Office Tab v9.81 (edit multiple files within a single tabbed window)
- Previous versions uninstallers (Office 2003, 2007)

Installation

- Delete any previously installed version using the provided uninstallers (recommended, not mandatory)
- Mount / burn / extract ISO file
- Install Office 2010
- Activate using Microsoft Toolkit / KMSpico (recommended)

Optional

- Classic Menu for Office v5.85 (adds Office 2003 type toolbars and menus to Office 2013)
- Office Tab v9.81 (edit multiple files within a single tabbed window)

OS Requirements

- Windows XP with SP3 (excluding 64-bit editions)
- Windows Vista SP1 / 7 / 8 /10
- Windows Server 2003 with SP2 and MSXML 6.0 (excluding 64-bit edition)
- Windows Server 2003 R2 / 2008 / 2008 R2 / 2012
